{
  "stem": "3658.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anybody that stayed behind a little bit, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they couldn't walk so fast, they just shot him and just left him in the gutter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was-- I didn't know how far it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But since then, I found out that it was about 30 kilometers, or 30 miles, I'm not sure which, from Gusen to Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And imagine people that can't--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--walk, that can hardly drag themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even remember getting much food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't even remember getting much food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they must have given us, when we stopped, some, some something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the thing that I remember very vividly, we went on the hill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's called today-- it's called-- they gave it a name, and I didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The hill-- it's some special name they gave it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words-- I can't remember the name because there was a massacre there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we got to that hill, we stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We slept at night, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the ground?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the ground.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the ground, on an open field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the shooting was all night long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But shooting at us, non-stop all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were-- you can imagine the ones that-- we were dead tired after walking for miles and miles and miles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We slept always in the open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, when they said, [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I pushed my friend next to me, that I knew, that we walked together, to get up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He'd been shot?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What, were they just taking pot shots at the crowd?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just shooting like we were dogs, not even.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a terrible, terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the morning, when you woke up, you got up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you looked around you.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
